  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"RLKTQ-tT\"><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=703006380&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">生理性别<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>绝大部分人并不知道——基本上是有点毛病（各种意义）的人才会去查染色体，（检验基因是否正常表达的医学检测更贵）</p><p data-pid=\"RkhclnT1\"><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=703006380&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">心理性别<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>全靠主观认同——就算给个心理量表我也见过为了想要结果背答案的大聪明</p><p data-pid=\"dD32PwDh\"><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=703006380&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">社会性别<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>我觉得能分出来1024种以上——毕竟有人拿<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=703006380&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%80%A7%E5%BE%81&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">第一性征<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>而不是<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=703006380&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">基因检测<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>作为性别划分标准的，在其中一方充分说服另一方之前，就可以分出：第一性征女xx正常表达，第一性征女xx不正常表达，第一性征男xy正常表达，第一性征男xy不正常表达这四种情况（实际上不正常表达的范围太广了还能进一步细分）</p><p data-pid=\"JUVUpW8i\">要是有人规定喜欢“标准”男性的是女性喜欢“标准”女性的是男性（指伊朗）——好，分类翻倍</p><p data-pid=\"Et1niMTw\">要是还有社会共识觉得某性别不准穿某种衣服，某性别不准留某种发型——好，再翻倍</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"RxaXY9G4\">所以这三个稀里糊涂的东西哪个能成为“决定性因素”啊</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
